Package: microbialForecast
Type: Package
Title: Spatio-temporal Forecasting of Soil Microbiomes
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Zoey", "Werbin", 
                  email = "zrwerbin@bu.edu", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "YOUR-ORCID-ID"))
Description: A comprehensive toolkit for spatio-temporal forecasting of soil 
    microbiomes using hierarchical Bayesian state-space models. Provides 
    functions for data preparation, model fitting, forecasting, and evaluation 
    of relative abundance patterns for taxonomic and functional groups across 
    environmental gradients.
